Press "=" to switch from classify vector to not classify vector
Press "b" to switch from Lerp average to log-spiral average
Press "2" to show the vector field on the center of the triangles
Press "5" to show the single trace
Press "4" to toggle on or off the colored triangle
Press "6" to show traces and samples
Press "7" to toggle on or off showing the continuous points on the traces
Press "8" to generate new mesh on the traces
Press "9" to show the colored edges which are on the traces

